        See who's <span class="bold-italic">actually</span> doing the work between sessions.
      </h2>
      <p class="pain">
        You can't tell who trained and who didn't.
      </p>
      <p class="solution">
        Squad Pulse shows sessions logged, compliance with assigned plans, and who's stalling.
        One scannable roster — three batched queries on the back end, regardless of squad size.
